	<h2 class="story">
		

		

		
		

		

		

		

		<span id="title-174636604" class="story-title"> <a   href="//slashdot.org/story/24/07/31/1325235/delta-ceo-says-crowdstrike-microsoft-outage-cost-the-airline-500-million">Delta CEO Says CrowdStrike-Microsoft Outage Cost the Airline $500 Million</a> <span class=" no extlnk"><a class="story-sourcelnk" href="https://www.cnbc.com/2024/07/31/delta-ceo-crowdstrike-microsoft-outage-cost-the-airline-500-million.html"  title="External link - https://www.cnbc.com/2024/07/31/delta-ceo-crowdstrike-microsoft-outage-cost-the-airline-500-million.html" target="_blank"> (cnbc.com) </a></span></span>

		
		
